ran a marathon and had a positive experience.  She planned on running a half
marathon six months from her marathon.  She eased up on her training since she
was confident about running a full marathon.  As a result, the half marathon was
very hard.

How am I like that?

I served a mission, but now that I am in real life there is a temptation to be
lax on some of the principles I practiced.

