Not physical at this time.

In millenium will be physical (two world captials).

\subsection{Why Ephraim?}
Ephraim had the birthright.  This is simbolic of the rest of the tribes
receiving their birthright from the tribe of Ephraim.
The oxen in the temple simbolize Joseph bringing the tribes the gospel.
Also recall that Joseph saved his brothers from the famine.




