\subsection{Holy Ghost and the Plan of Salvation}

{\it Thought, 2013.04.14:} In the {\it Gospel Principles} manual,
Holy Ghost is Chapter 7.  The previous 6 chapters are heavy chapters
about God, our pre-mortal existence, agency, and the Fall of Adam
and Eve.  I think that Holy Ghost comes in at this point because of
how essential it is to the Plan of Salvation.  We are cut off from
God's presence; how are we to know what is right and wrong?  How are
we to know the truth?  The Holy Ghost provides just enough to show
us the truth.

