\subsection{Scripture Chain}
\begin{itemize}
 \item 2 Ne. 2:25: ``men are that they might have joy''
 \item Opposition is necessary that joy might exist: 2 Ne. 2:11, Alma 60:13
 \item 2 Ne. 2:3: God ``shall consecrate [our] afflictions for [our] gain''.
 \item Happiness comes from obedience to the commandments: Mosiah 2:41, Alma
41:10
 \item We must repent to become happier
 \item Our body permits us to have joy: D\&C 93:33
