\noindent Thoughts 2010.10.15:
My scripture study is for my personal edification.  It is not for prideful
purposes.

\noindent Thoughts 2013.08.24
Just as we are asked to sacrifice time for the Sabbath day, we are
asked to sacrifice time to study the scriptures.  The natural man in
us would rather spend our time on fun things, or even on work.  I
know that the Lord blesses us when we sacrifice our time to fulfill
his will.  Further, I know that the Lord blesses us when we have a
sincere scripture study.

